    <title lang="pl">Scott Ross - Traces of a Shooting Star 1951 - 1989</title>
    <desc lang="pl">Scott Ross - Traces of a Shooting Star 1951 - 1989 Scott on the Ross, about the recording of the 555 sonatas of Domenico Scarlatti Villeneuve lez Avignon, Tinel, April 1985 Produced by Bernard Tournois and Martina Catella Les maîtres de musique - Works by Domenico Scarlatti and Padre Antonio Soler Domenico Scarlatti 1685 - 1757 Sonata in D minor K 1 Sonata in A major K 6 Sonata in F sharp minor K 25 Sonata in B minor K 27 Sonata in E major K 380 Sonata in E major K 381 Sonata in A major K 208 Sonata in A major K 209 Antonio Soler 1729 - 1783 2 sonatas in D minor R 49 &amp; R 15 2 sonatas in F major R 56 &amp; R 69 Fandango R 146 Paris, Théâtre du Ranelagh, May 7, 1988 Directed by Georges Bessonnet Digital restoration 2024.</desc>
